om-apple-piazza-liberty/1478181719|title=Up Next (Live From Apple Piazza Liberty) by Bad Bunny|website=[[Apple Music]]|accessdate=February 6, 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Singles ==\n=== As lead artist ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\" border=\"1\"\n|+ List of singles as lead artist, with selected chart positions and certifications, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:17.5em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"| [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard Hot 100|US]]<br><ref name=\"US\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/bad-bunny/chart-history/HSI|title=Bad Bunny Chart History (Hot 100)|work=Billboard|accessdate=February 3, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Hot Latin Songs|US<br>Latin]]<br><ref name=\"USLatin\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/bad-bunny/chart-history/HTL|title=Bad Bunny Chart History (Hot Latin Songs)|work=Billboard|accessdate=April 7, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Argentina Hot 100|ARG]]<br><ref name=\"ARG\">Peak positions in Argentina:\n* All except noted: {{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/bad-bunny/chart-history/ARG|title=Bad Bunny Chart History (Billboard Argentina Hot 100)|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=April 8, 2020}}\n* \"[[Estamos Bien]]\": {{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com.ar/chart/hot100/2018-10-12|title=Argentina Hot 100 \u2013 Semana del 20 de Octubre del 2018|work=[[Billboard Argentina]]|language=Spanish|accessdate=October 18, 2018}}\n* \"Dura (Remix)\" and \"Te Bot\u00e9 (Remix)\" : {{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com.ar/chart/hot100/2018-10-05|t